# Backup and Recovery Policy
### Small Business Information Security Starter Kit

---

> **Before you use this template:** This is a starting point, not a finished document. Read through it, delete anything that doesn't apply to your business, fill in the highlighted sections [IN BRACKETS], and write it in your own words where it makes sense to do so. A policy that sounds like you will get followed. A policy that sounds like a solicitor probably won't.

